wnload PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533722\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533722\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xgv1665702734252.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgv1665702734252.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgv1665702734252.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xgv1665702734252\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Sybase Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__sybase_connector_options_173110\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can assign connector options by setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span> in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__topic_d59147e1_d59148e1_d59149e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59150e1_d59151e1_d59152e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n            n}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__topic_d39237e1_d39238e1_d39239e1_d39240e1_d39241e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d829207e74\">\n                        \n Options\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26531e1_d26532e1_d26533e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iwb1665702734332.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iwb1665702734332.html\" title=\"Create tables with all pages locking.\">allpages locking</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26537e1_d26538e1_d26539e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tke1665702734474.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tke1665702734474.html\" title=\"Set default character set used by the Sybase open client.\">charset</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26534e1_d26535e1_d26536e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wnv1665702734401.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wnv1665702734401.html\" title=\"Enables data to be correctly retrieved when the length of a numeric database field is longer than the length defined in the Uniface field interface definition.\">convert numeric</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26540e1_d26541e1_d26542e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"stv1665702734543.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/stv1665702734543.html\" title=\"Create tables with data pages locking.\">datapages locking</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26543e1_d26544e1_d26545e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ovd1665702964846.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ovd1665702964846.html\" title=\"Enable Sybase referential integrity controls.\">dbms ri</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26546e1_d26547e1_d26548e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"neh1665702734617.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/neh1665702734617.html\" title=\"Disable textpointer check during Fetch requests.\">delay textptr check</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26549e1_d26550e1_d26551e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hrb1665702734690.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hrb1665702734690.html\" title=\"Access table and field names when they are in uppercase.\">disable lower</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26552e1_d26553e1_d26554e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zqk1665702686078.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zqk1665702686078.html\" title=\"Disable support for numeric and identity data types.\">disable numerics</a>\n</li> <li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26558e1_d26559e1_d26560e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bft1665702734828.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bft1665702734828.html\" title=\"Disable the Sybase connector check for stored procedures.\">disable proc check</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26555e1_d26556e1_d26557e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cso1665702734759.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cso1665702734759.html\" title=\"Disable the use of all stored procedures.\">disable procs</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26561e1_d26562e1_d26563e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"liy1665702686148.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/liy1665702686148.html\" title=\"Generate dump transaction statements in the SQL scripts created by the Create Table facility.\">dump tran</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26564e1_d26565e1_d26566e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dsl1665702734898.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dsl1665702734898.html\" title=\"Control the actual value inserted into a Sybase identity field.\">identity insert</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26567e1_d26568e1_d26569e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ozf1665702734970.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ozf1665702734970.html\" title=\"Adds double quotes around field and table names and sets the Sybase option quoted_identifier on.\">keyword</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26570e1_d26571e1_d26572e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ead1665702665322.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ead1665702665322.html\" title=\"Specify the language used by the Sybase SQL Server for error messages.\">language</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26573e1_d26574e1_d26575e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmz1665702706437.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmz1665702706437.html\" title=\"Set the Sybase transaction isolation level.\">lock level</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26576e1_d26577e1_d26578e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bvv1665702930308.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bvv1665702930308.html\" title=\"Set the period a database operation will wait for a database lock to be released.\">maxlockwait</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26579e1_d26580e1_d26581e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lkm1665702966505.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lkm1665702966505.html\" title=\"Enable multibyte character sets.\">multi byte</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26582e1_d26583e1_d26584e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vxw1665702686009.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vxw1665702686009.html\" title=\"Create tables with row level locking.\">row level locks</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26585e1_d26586e1_d26587e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrs1665702735046.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrs1665702735046.html\" title=\"Set the limit for the number of bytes in the fixed-length portion of a record.\">row limit</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26588e1_d26589e1_d26590e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vtt1665702967459.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vtt1665702967459.html\" title=\"Set the size of each step in the Uniface stepped hitlist.\">step size</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26591e1_d26592e1_d26593e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xof1665702735116.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xof1665702735116.html\" title=\"Strip trailing spaces off char field values returned by the sql ProcScript statement.\">strip spaces</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26594e1_d26595e1_d26596e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kly1665702735187.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kly1665702735187.html\" title=\"Set the Sybase packet size.\">tds_packetsize</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26597e1_d26598e1_d26599e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jqf1665702735257.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqf1665702735257.html\" title=\"Drop and create all tables and procedures.\">U4 upgrade</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26600e1_d26601e1_d26602e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tlc1665702735327.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tlc1665702735327.html\" title=\"Enable or disable Unicode support in the SYB connector.\">unicode</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26603e1_d26604e1_d26605e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xqq1665702735396.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xqq1665702735396.html\" title=\"Sets the length of overflow table segments to 8000 characters.\">widetable overflow</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__topic_d39242e1_d39243e1_d39244e1_d39245e1_d39246e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d829207e347\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59159e1_d59160e1_d59161e1\">Most connector options enable or disable a specific feature by setting the option. Some options have a numeric parameter. This parameter must be a non-negative decimal integer (every numeric option has a default value). The range of valid values is option-specific.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59162e1_d59163e1_d59164e1\">Every connector option can be specified using either a long format, which is readable, or a short format, which allows you to set many options in the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span> assignment.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__topic_d39247e1_d39248e1_d39249e1_d39250e1_d39251e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d829207e362\">\n                        \n Syntax Rules\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59168e1_d59169e1_d59170e1\">The syntax rules for <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span> are as follows:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26606e1_d26607e1_d26608e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59171e1_d59172e1_d59173e1\">The assignment can be no longer than one line in the assignment file.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26609e1_d26610e1_d26611e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59174e1_d59175e1_d59176e1\">Each option may be specified once, either in long format or in short format, not both. Options in long format may be mixed with other options in short format.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26612e1_d26613e1_d26614e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59177e1_d59178e1_d59179e1\">The order in which the options are specified is not significant.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26615e1_d26616e1_d26617e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59180e1_d59181e1_d59182e1\">Multiple options must be separated by a comma.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26618e1_d26619e1_d26620e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59183e1_d59184e1_d59185e1\">Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26621e1_d26622e1_d26623e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59186e1_d59187e1_d59188e1\">Options are not case-dependent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26624e1_d26625e1_d26626e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59189e1_d59190e1_d59191e1\">All options have the form directive = value.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26627e1_d26628e1_d26629e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59192e1_d59193e1_d59194e1\">Instead of the equal sign (=), a colon (:) can be used. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS = disable numerics = on, language: french, step size: 14</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__topic_d39252e1_d39253e1_d39254e1_d39255e1_d39256e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d829207e430\">\n                        \n TM support\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59198e1_d59199e1_d59200e1\">For TM-enabled logon paths, the following connector options are not supported:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26630e1_d26631e1_d26632e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59201e1_d59202e1_d59203e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">tds</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">packetsize</code>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26633e1_d26634e1_d26635e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59204e1_d59205e1_d59206e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">lock</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">level</code>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__li_d26636e1_d26637e1_d26638e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgv1665702734252__p_d59207e1_d59208e1_d59209e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">timeout</code>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533722\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533722\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Sybase Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Sybase Connector Options You can assign connector options by setting USYS$SYB_PARAMS in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. USYS$SYB_PARAMS Option { , Option n} Options allpages locking charset convert numeric datapages locking dbms ri delay textptr check disable lower disable numerics disable proc check disable procs dump tran identity insert keyword language lock level maxlockwait multi byte row level locks row limit step size strip spaces tds_packetsize U4 upgrade unicode widetable overflow Description Most connector options enable or disable a specific feature by setting the option. Some options have a numeric parameter. This parameter must be a non-negative decimal integer (every numeric option has a default value). The range of valid values is option-specific. Every connector option can be specified using either a long format, which is readable, or a short format, which allows you to set many options in the USYS$SYB_PARAMS assignment. Syntax Rules The syntax rules for USYS$SYB_PARAMS are as follows: The assignment can be no longer than one line in the assignment file. Each option may be specified once, either in long format or in short format, not both. Options in long format may be mixed with other options in short format. The order in which the options are specified is not significant. Multiple options must be separated by a comma. Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs. Options are not case-dependent. All options have the form directive = value. Instead of the equal sign (=), a colon (:) can be used. For example: USYS$SYB_PARAMS = disable numerics = on, language: french, step size: 14 Copy TM support For TM-enabled logon paths, the following connector options are not supported: tds packetsize lock level timeout Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}